# Codline AI - Recommended Write Order

1. chat/memory.py
   - TextMemory
   - SummaryMemory

2. chat/prompts.py
   - System prompts
   - ChatPromptTemplate builder

3. chat/llm.py
   - generate_reply(messages)
   - summarize_conversation(text)

4. chat/chatbot.py
   - Chatbot class
   - ask(user_input) method
   - maybe_update_summary()

5. main.py
   - Simple CLI loop
   - Hook into Chatbot.ask()
